strings:
<voice_0x01001753><se_high>Princess Medea: Thank you, <hero>.
I will forever be in your debt.

<voice_0x01001754><se_high>Princess Medea: You always come to my aid,
whenever I'm in need.

<voice_0x01001755><se_high>Princess Medea: But let us make this the last time, shall we?
I must learn to look after myself.
<voice_0x01001756><se_high>Princess Medea: After all, I shan't have you at my beck and call forever...
<voice_0x01001757><se_high>Princess Medea: Captain <endash> you are dismissed, with immediate effect! You may consider that a direct order from your princess.
<voice_0x01001758><se_high>Princess Medea: You have done your duty.

<voice_0x0100175A><se_high>Princess Medea: Follow your dreams.
You have your own life to live.
Say you will.

<voice_0x0100175B><se_high>Princess Medea: Hee hee, I know you so well...
But then we did grow up together.
<voice_0x0100175C><se_high>Princess Medea: There's someone else who needs you at her side now, isn't there?
<voice_0x0100175E><se_high>Princess Medea: You would rather stay with me?
<voice_0x0100175F><se_high>Princess Medea: Then you must be her protector from now on.

<voice_0x01001760><se_high>Princess Medea: And I will pray with all my heart for
your happiness.

<voice_0x01001761><se_high>Princess Medea: There's no need to pretend.
I meant what I said.

<voice_0x01001762><se_high>Princess Medea: You don't have to devote your life to me.
It's time for you to follow your heart.
<voice_0x01001763><se_high>Princess Medea: I... I'm so happy to hear you say that...
<voice_0x01001764><se_high>Princess Medea: I am so very lucky to have you.
